column3: <blip> Greetings, <Split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)/>. Thank you for agreeing to knock Thiuna into shape.
<blip> Be kindly informed that your every action is currently being recorded. <buzz> Remember to smile.
<blip> Glory be to Allag. Long may she endure.
<blip> Water and nodes do not mix. As a precautionary measure, I must maintain a safe distance from amaro.
<blip> Be advised that forced shutdowns may result in corrupted data. It is recommended that you perform regular backups.
<blip> All data pertaining to <Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight> has been encrypted under the Protect protocol. <buzz> Your personal information is safe with me.
